Name: W. T. B.
About the game: This is a branded anniversary clicker! In this game you will use the logic and sleight of hand to combine red, blue and green in the corresponding holes. Under relaxing music, you are counting on several steps forward rearrange the colors in places so that they coincide. The longer you do this, the higher the speed of the figures and the complexity of the game! Features: - Hardcore clicker; - Branded game from W.T.B .; - Relaxing soundtrack; - 'It's easy to understand, but it's impossible to pass.' Share your records with help screenshots and win your friends on Steam!
